kpi_info.title: MAC-D SETUP ATTEMPT FOR HSDPA
kpi_info.use: The number of attempted radio link setups/reconfigurations for HSDPA MAC-d flow. UPDATED: When the RNC sends NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP REQUEST or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION PREPARE with information to configure HSDPA MAC-d flow for the radio link.
